s that can be made arbitrarily small, at the\nprice of processing a sufficiently large number of channel uses together.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Jun 2013 20:54:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 27 Jun 2016 04:38:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-17"}
